_sText:
I made this map to try to look like cartoons, but i dont think i got that across but its a REALLY fun map. there are many traps, and pac-man, and the 4 ghosts!

Custom Materials by: Drumbtr

Have Fun!


Change Log: 
dr_cartoon - first release
dr_cartoon_b2 - fixed glitches with shortcutting
dr_cartoon_b3 - added some goodies for players to play with, fixed combine trap, made path break, added lasers, fixed some visual glitches
dr_cartoon_b3FixedSky - fixed the sky (who would have guessed that?)
dr_cartoon_b4 - balenced traps
